videos.description: Kaleb Wesson hits a wide-open 3-pointer to cut High Point's lead to 3.
videos.headline: Wesson sinks 3 to pull Ohio State within 3

videos.description: Ohio State's C.J. Jackson drives to the basket for a quick layup, drawing a foul in the process.
videos.headline: Jackson ties game with basket and foul

videos.description: Kyle Young comes up with a dunk to give the Buckeyes a comfortable lead over the Panthers.
videos.headline: Young smashes dunk to keep Ohio State rolling
